innies.schedule:
LOAD 1
SHIFT 3 TIMES
MULTIPLY 2
WAFFLE
END_SHIFT

LOAD 0
SHIFT 2 TIMES
ADD HELLY
END_SHIFT
WAFFLE

LOAD 100
WELLNESS_CHECK HELLY > ANY OF [MARK]
CONDITIONAL_ADD [HELLY, MARK] IF MARK > 10
WAFFLE

LOAD 1
SHIFT 4 TIMES
ADD IRVING
WAFFLE
END_SHIFT

LOAD 0
ADD [HELLY, MARK, IRVING, BURT]
MULTIPLY 2
WELLNESS_CHECK BURT > ALL OF [HELLY, MARK, IRVING]
WAFFLE
